author: @ImportData1
text: Time management is one of the most important skills! One of the things I did in college to stay focused & productive was to have a solid wall between the studying/productive time and my leisure time. For instance, I would be productive from 9am-1pm and reward myself by doing something fun (playing games, playing with my dog, etc.) for about an hour! Then I would get back to the productive time from 2pm-7pm and reward myself again!
